/i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F01%2F20180108_PN_SUBWAY_NO_PANTS_012.jpg&h=7662211e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/01/20180108_PN_SUBWAY_NO_PANTS_013.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F01%2F20180108_PN_SUBWAY_NO_PANTS_013.jpg&h=bac82180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/01/20180108_PN_SUBWAY_NO_PANTS_014.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F01%2F20180108_PN_SUBWAY_NO_PANTS_014.jpg&h=b00d2899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/01/20180108_PN_SUBWAY_NO_PANTS_015.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F01%2F20180108_PN_SUBWAY_NO_PANTS_015.jpg&h=7ca72807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/01/20180108_PN_SUBWAY_NO_PANTS_016.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F01%2F20180108_PN_SUBWAY_NO_PANTS_016.jpg&h=f2282fe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/01/20180108_PN_SUBWAY_NO_PANTS_017.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F01%2F20180108_PN_SUBWAY_NO_PANTS_017.jpg&h=3e822f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天寒地凍他們搭車不穿褲子，看起來還若無其事，原來是參加年度「地鐵盛事」。<br />\n歐美國家正受寒流侵襲，仍有不少民眾無懼零下低溫響應「地鐵無褲日」。<br />\n<br />\n「地鐵無褲日」（No Pants Subway Ride）顧名思義即是不穿褲子搭車，然後盡可能扮作若無其事。參與者要假裝彼此不認識，除了沒穿外褲，他們仍會穿上冬天衣服，圍上頸巾等。<br />\n<br />\n這項即興發起的惡作劇活動2002年由民間團體Improve Everywhere在美國紐約發起，至今已第16年，參加人數年年上升，而且遍及世界各地，由一開始7人發起，到今年單是紐約就有超過4000人響應；此外，波士頓、倫敦、柏林、布拉格和耶路撒冷等近30個大城市都有民眾參加。<br />\n<br />\n活動發起人說並非要賣弄色情，參加的人也不能穿上令人感到冒犯的內褲，也不會配合任何示威活動，活動是希望讓每天過著繁忙無趣生活的民眾破舊立新，為生活增添更多趣味。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2737255-無懼寒冬！歐美民眾齊響應「地鐵無褲日」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F2737255-%E7%84%A1%E6%87%BC%E5%AF%92%E5%86%AC%EF%BC%81%E6%AD%90%E7%BE%8E%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E9%BD%8A%E9%9F%BF%E6%87%89%E3%80%8C%E5%9C%B0%E9%90%B5%E7%84%A1%E8%A4%B2%E6%97%A5%E3%80%8D&d=U%2BkWzTdhjVf0XVIsnGw%2Bv0zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=932984f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2737255-無懼寒冬！歐美民眾齊響應「地鐵無褲日」</a>"},{"pid":"75d391ad1b997d9b92177ddd1c016847187d8c51","tid":524007,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:01:41.000Z","msg":"又扮撚哂野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d4c5a20bbbddc8561a939c675b4686057150d8","tid":524007,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:03:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef705e9b431d17360b85650e2331110357352dd4","tid":524007,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52d4c5a20bbbddc8561a939c675b4686057150d8","tid":524007,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:03:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"香港都唔得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}